MST THEORY -->A spanning tree is a subset of edges that:

1. Connects all vertices
2. Contains no cycle
3. Uses exactly V-1 edges

IF EDGES HAVE WEIGHT, THEN FOR MIN COST WE HAVE MIN SPANNING TREE. 

Properties of MST

For graph with V vertices:
Connected
No cycle
V-1 edges
